product_title: Mama Koala One Size Baby Washable Reusable Pocket Cloth Diapers, 6 Pack with 6 One Size Microfiber Inserts (Jagger)
product_description:
Product Details

Mama Koala cloth diaper is a one-size pocket diaper that fits most babies 8-35lbs. The diaper has an outer layer of breathable, waterproof thermoplastic polyurethane(TPU) to keep wetness in, and an inner layer of high quality suede cloth that wicks moisture away from baby's delicate skin, and provides a trim fit.

Included 6 FREE adjustable inserts made of 3 layers of thirsty microfiber.

Wash and Care

Shake off poop into the toilet.
Put wet or soiled diapers in a dry pail.
Pre-wash with cold water and no detergent.
Do a regular wash in hot water (40C/104F max) with detergent.
Rinse warm twice.
Tumble dry low.
No bleach. No fabric softener.

Tips:
Wash diapers and inserts prior to first use.
We recommend washing every 1-2 days.
Change baby's diaper every 2-3 hours.
product_bullet_point:
NO LEAKS - Waterproof and breathable TPU outer, super soft and stay dry suede cloth inner protects baby from moisture
GROWS WITH YOUR CHILD - One size (8-35lbs) with 3x3 rise snaps to customize for the perfect fit
SAVE MONEY AND REDUCE WASTE - one size cloth diapers and inserts are simple, economical and eco-friendly
ULTRA ABSORBENT - Your order includes 6 one-size 3-layer microfiber inserts. They are light weight yet highly absorbent. The inserts with snaps or folds are shipped randomly. Designation or exchange services are not available.
MANUFACTURER PROMISE - Quality guarantee and 5-star customer service. If you are not 100% completely satisfied, give us a call or email us and we'll make it right. All returned items in good condition will be donated.

product_title: SSK Aluminum Hard Drive Docking Station, USB 3.0 to SATA Dual Bay External HDD Dock Caddy Reader for 2.5 & 3.5 inch SATA HDD SSD, with UASP Offline Cloner/Duplicator Function(2x16TB Supports)
product_description:
Product specifications:
Product Name:SSK Aluminum USB 3.0 to SATA Dual Bay External Hard Drive Docking Station for 2.5/3.5 Inch HDD SSD SATA with UASP Offline Clone Duplicator Function (2x16TB Supports)
To use Hard Drive Offline Clone Function:
1. Insert Source Disk into hard drive bay A, then insert Target Disk into hard drive bay B.
2. Make sure that the USB cable is disconnected from your computer.
3. Connect power supply and switch on power.
4. Hold down the CLONE button , release when you see all lights flashing.
5. Then quickly press the CLONE Button.
6. A Yellow LED will flash on 25% indicating that the cloning process has begun.
7. The cloning process is complete when you hear the'Bang noise'for three times (25%-100%).
8. Finally press the power switch to the OFF position and eject your drives.
Features:
1.SSK Aluminum Dual Bay External Hard Drive Docking Station can copy your files from one disk to another without computer support.
2. The Dual Dock provides simultaneous access to both drives, uses external power for stable drive performance and supports hot-swapping so you won't need to reboot your computer.
3.Supports UASP technology,UASP is a new transport protocol, which can increase data transfer speed, up to 70% faster than conventional USB 3.0. Transfer 1G files only within 10 seconds.
Package includes:
1x SSK DK103 Docking Station;
1x USB 3.0 Cable
1x 12V/2.5A Power Adapter;
1x User Manual
product_bullet_point:
【Universal Compatibility】SSK USB3.0 SATA HDD docking station is compatible with all 2.5 inch and 3.5 inch SATA I/II/III HDD SSD; it supports UASP and transfer speed up to 5Gbps(USB3.0). LED indicator status display.
【Aluminum Shell】SSK HDD Dock with solid, shockproof & vibration-resistant aluminum shell, the external SATA HDD/SSD boasts efficient Heatsink to stay cool with low power consumption for reliable data transfers.
【Offline Clone】SSK Hard drive docking station supports offline clone duplicator function, it can be used to clone an existing hard drive without connecting to a computer, easy to duplicate data from one to another hard drive.
【32TB Capacity】SSK HDD enclosure can support 2x16TB hard drive simultaneously for 2.5/3.5 inch SATA I/II/III HDD/SSD with exquisite design. Plug and play,no driver needed and tool-free installation.
【Multi-OS Compatible】SSK USB3.0 2.5 3.5 HDD Dock is compatible with Windows XP / Vista / Windows 7 / Windows 8 / Windows 8.1 / Windows 10 Mac IOS 10.4 to 10.11 Linux Kernel 2.4.2 or higher versions.

Package Contents:
-3 Pcs Stamping Plates and 1 nail stamper and scraper (random color)

Instruction Of Nail Plates: 1. Apply base coat or regular polish on the nail ;
2. Apply the nail polish to desired image within a nail plate ;
3. Make a scraper leaned over 45 degrees and scrape excessive polish off quickly and strongly from inside to outside ;
4. Immediately press the stamper with a gentle rolling motion to pick up the design. The image is transferred on the nail stamp ;
5. Stamp the image on your nail with a gentle rolling motion. The image is transferred on your nail ;
6. Repeat the above steps for all of your nails ;
7. After stamping nail art, apply top coat for lasting wear.

Instruction Of Nail Stamper: 1. Apply base coat or regular polish on nail;
2. Apply nail polish to desired image within a plate;
3. Scrape across plate with the scraper to remove excessive polish;
4. Quickly press the stamper onto the plate to pick up the design;
5. Stamp the image onto your nail with a rolling motion or just press down

product_description: The Anatomy Lab miniature human skeleton model offers a great amount of anatomical detail for an entry-level mini skeleton model. The model delivers a fair amount of the detail when its compared to more expensive models. Make no mistake, this is a great basic and entry level skeleton! The skeletons arms and legs are both movable at all the major joint groupsFor the arm: the shoulders, elbows and wrists; and for the Leg: the hip sockets, knees and ankles all move. The toes and fingers do not offer any movement and the spine, neck and pelvis do not have any movement. Both legs are removable from the model, the arms do not detach from the skeleton. The skull cap and the jaw can remove from the skull, and the jaw offers natural movement. The model mounts to a white base that is 8 x 6 and it is held in place by a pelvically mounted rod. The skeleton stands 35 tall and weighs approximately 4 pounds.

product_title: AUUGUU Kids Dinosaur Race Car Track with Flexible Track, Dino Toys, Bridge, Ramps and 2 Race Car Toys – Prehistoric Race Track for Kids Age 3-5
product_description:
Resurrect the prehistoric age

The AUUGUU Dinosaur Race Car Track Set combines the fascinating world of the Cretaceous Period when the T-Rex and Triceratops roamed the Earth with present-day discovery toys. This 156-piece dinosaur play set includes 142 track pieces, 2 realistic dinosaur toys, 2 motorized toy cars, 4 plastic trees, a bridge, 2 ramps and a rushing double-door gate. Boys and girls will spend hours arranging the track in new arrangements and watching the cars whiz past dinosaur figures and up and down hills, escaping the jaws of these imposing creatures.

A new twist on race car toys

Our innovative flexible track pieces can be curved into a variety of configurations from traditional ovals to raised figure 8s, banked circles and rolling tracks. They are easily snapped and unsnapped by kids age 3 and older, helping to strengthen motor skills and hand-eye coordination even as they have fun playing. Kids will thrill at discovering new ways to incorporate the bridge, ramps and gate into the lay-outs to add exciting twists and turns to the race. Cars are battery-operated and can be used independently of the race track for other play.

Safety is our top priority

This premium dinosaur toy race track meets all US ASTM F 963 and European EN71 Toy Safety Standards. It is made with eco-friendly parts that are non-toxic and BPA-free for the well-being of your child. It would be a popular birthday or Christmas gift for boys and girls who love to build with their hands.

Introduce your child to a fun and fascinating prehistoric world. Add the AUUGUU Dinosaur Toy Car Track to your cart today.
product_bullet_point:
Awaken their primal instincts with this deluxe dinosaur track set by AUUGUU. The fun is non-stop as kids arrange the racetrack in various configurations with ramps, trees, a bridge and a gate to maneuver cars safely through and over.
156-Piece set includes 144 pieces of flexible track, 2 toy SUVs, 2 dinosaur figures, 2 ramps, a bridge, a gate and 4 plastic trees. Children exercise their imaginations and learn to problem-solve as they set up amazing dinosaur worlds indoors or outdoors.
Ignite their curiosity about the world and how it used to be as they examine the realistic T-Rex and Triceratops figures. Girls and boys can imagine these extinct behemoths menacing the passing cars and wreaking havoc on the tree-lined dinosaur car track.
Fun for all or even just for 1, our dinosaur car race track includes 2 motorized cars that each require 1 AA battery (not included). Children gain valuable socialization skills and learn how to self-entertain with this set of dinosaur toys for 3-year-old boys and girls.
Durable and non-toxic plastic dinosaur toy playset is environmentally-friendly, BPA-free and safe for children ages 3 and up. The AUUGUU Dinosaur Race Track has passed the highest US ASTM F 963 and European EN71 Toy Safety Standards.

product_title: BONECO - Air Washer W200 Humidifier & Purifier
product_description:
Trusted Swiss Company For Over 50 Years - BONECO products have been available in North America since 2001. You can depend on the reliability of BONECO, whose parent company has been a trusted Swiss company and manufacturer since 1956. BONECO uses high-quality components, such as a non-corrosive titanium membrane that provides years of trouble-free operation.

Simplicity of operation and maintenance are what define the W200 air washer. Two performance levels can be selected with the turn-switch. For cleaning, the water base and the evaporation elements can simply be placed in the dishwasher or washing machine. It is also possible to add scented oils, for those looking for a scented room. An LED display lights up when the water base is empty. The air washer then switches off automatically and can be filled with fresh water. Also, the understated and modern design of the W200 fits in every living room or office, and customers value its exceptional performance.

The Air Washers uses water to humidify and wash the air. Specially textured evaporator mats turn in the water, which adds moisture to the air by evaporation. The water acts as a natural filter, which washes the air of impurities (e.g.- dust, pollen, and particle-bound odors). The self-regulating evaporation principle ensures the correct humidity in the room, as the air automatically draws as much moisture as it needs at any given moment. Air Washers can be used all year round and are especially suited for allergy sufferers, due to their natural cleaning principle, without the need for additives.
product_bullet_point:
DUAL FUNCTION: This machine washes and humidifies a room's air. The evaporator mat rotates through the water enriching the air with moisture. The water serves as a natural filter that frees air of impurities (such as particles like pollen & dust).
TWO OPERATION MODES: Two operation modes for Day: which enables maximum output or Night: for quiet operation. There is also a smart automatic shut off when the tank is empty, and it is a low energy consumption appliance.
CONVENIENT HANDLING: Thanks to the direct filling of the water base. The understated & modern design of the W200 fits in every bedroom or office, & customers value its exceptional performance. Enjoy high-quality components with long service life.
HUMIDIFIER DIFFUSER: There is an integrated fragrance container for essential oils for additional well-being. Fill your office, living room, or bedside with your favorite scent combo to help with comfort and enrichment of your space.
EASY TO CLEAN AND USE: Most of the parts can just be placed in the dishwasher or washing machine, saving hand-scrubbing time. The easy-to-use knob allows you to switch between the 2 performance levels.

DUAL FUNCTION: This machine washes and humidifies a room's air. The evaporator mat rotates through the water enriching the air with moisture. The water serves as a natural filter that frees air of impurities (such as particles like pollen & dust). TWO OPERATION MODES: Two operation modes for Day: which enables maximum output or Night: for quiet operation. There is also a smart automatic shut off when the tank is empty, and it is a low energy consumption appliance. CONVENIENT HANDLING: Thanks to the direct filling of the water base. The understated & modern design of the W200 fits in every bedroom or office, & customers value its exceptional performance. Enjoy high-quality components with long service life. HUMIDIFIER DIFFUSER: There is an integrated fragrance container for essential oils for additional well-being. Fill your office, living room, or bedside with your favorite scent combo to help with comfort and enrichment of your space. EASY TO CLEAN AND USE: Most of the parts can just be placed in the dishwasher or washing machine, saving hand-scrubbing time. The easy-to-use knob allows you to switch between the 2 performance levels.

product_title: Eva Naturals Vitamin C Serum Plus 2% Retinol, 3.5% Niacinamide, 5% Hyaluronic Acid, 2% Salicylic Acid, 10% MSM, 20% Vitamin C - Skin Clearing Serum - Anti-Aging Skin Repair, Face Serum (1 oz)
product_description:
Protect, Repair and Revitalize Your Skin!

How many steps are in your skincare routine? With cleansing and moisturizing, exfoliating and spot-treatments, most of us use way too many products. Things don't have to be so complicated!

Skin Clearing Serum by Eva Naturals is an all-in-one formula that simplifies skincare! We brought together some of the most potent ingredients to address a wide range of skin concerns. Vitamin C is the star of our blend as it offers anti-aging benefits like UV protection and helps repair sun-damaged skin. We paired it with Hyaluronic Acid, which provides incredible hydration, for smooth, younger-looking skin!

Because blemishes pop up at any age, we included the cleansing powers of Retinol! It gives pores a deep clean, warding off breakouts and minimizing the appearance of pores. Niacinamide works to reduce redness and inflammation, while Salicylic Acids offers gentle exfoliation your skin will love!
product_bullet_point:
Best Anti Aging Serum - Loaded with antioxidants, our Vitamin C Serum helps protect against UV rays while repairing sun-damaged skin. For an anti-aging boost, Hyaluronic Acid provides incredible hydration by holding up to 1000 times its weight in water!
Glowing Complexion - Acne and other skin conditions leave your complexion looking red and uneven. The Niacinamide found in our formula supports healthy skin by naturally reducing inflammation and soothing troubled skin for an overall more even skin tone! This is also an effective dark spot corrector and hyperpigmentation treatment.
Best Acne Treatment - When pores are clogged with dirt and oil, they become larger and more visible. Retinol works to cleanse the pores, thereby making them appear smaller. Add to that the exfoliating effects of Salicylic Acid, and our serum is ready to fight blemishes and improve acne prone skin. A powerful alternative for products like Retin A, aha serums, hydroquinone and other retinoid products on the market.
Natural Skincare - Packed with vitamins, essential oils, and organic ingredients like Aloe, our organic vitamin c serum is an adult acne treatment and dry skin facial treatment all in one! We focus on natural ingredients to keep our formula safe and effective for all skin types.

product_title: SORARA Outdoor Louvered Pergola 10' × 13' Aluminum Dark Bronze Outdoor Deck Garden Patio Gazebo with Adjustable Roof
product_description:
Sorara Outdoor Living has created a louvered pergola system that extends your living space outdoors. 

The Mirador’s patented louvered pergola design allows you to utilize your space on sunny days and even when its raining. You control the amount of sunlight you want with our premium ergonomically designed louver wand. 

When the rain starts you do not have to retreat to the indoors. Simply close the louver roof and let Mirador’s integrated guttering system protect you from the elements. 

Whether you are covering a seating area, hot tub, or even your favorite BBQ grill, Mirador is the perfect choice. Invite your neighbors, family and friends over for a day of relaxation under Mirador. 

Constructed of a heavy gauge aluminum frame and sturdy powder coated steel louvers, Mirador received a 2020 Red Dot award for its innovative design. There are no visible fasteners to distract from its sleek appearance. Step-by-Step assembly and installation instructions are easy to understand and helpful videos are available as well.
product_bullet_point:
Premium material construction:Mirador is constructed of a powder coated aluminum frame and steel louvers that resist the elements and is TUV rated and designed to last for years of enjoyment.
Easy to Assemble and Install: Innovative “floorplan” instructions and online video aids are available to guide you.
Prefabricated Rails and Louvers: Assembly requires no special rivets or welds and is structurally sound.
Multi-functional: You are in control of the elements. You select the amount of sun you let in and you also have freedom from rainouts.
Coverage area: The 10’ x 13’ size provides 130 sq. ft. of direct coverage from the sun or rain.

product_description: Asutra has gone the extra mile by creating a 100% silk eye pillow that we hand-fill with organic lavender and flax seed to produce a weighted sleep mask. Both the pillow and muslin pouch have zippers, so you can fill the pouch to the weight you desire. You can also skip the muslin bag and fill the eye pillow directly for a more conforming feeling. For a bonus, we’ve added a free soothing eye gel mask – which is a $7.95 value. This eye gel mask can help to relieve eye fatigue and is very simple to use - simply place it in the fridge for a soothing cooling effect. This eye gel mask is also fully adjustable to fit everyone and comes packaged with your purchase.

product_title: 1 1/4 Inch Diamond Drill Bit Tile Hole Saw Ceramic Porcelain Quartz Granite Glass Fish Tank Kitchen Bathroom Shower Faucet Installation 1.25 Inches Single Pack
product_description:
This listing is for individual diamond hole saw - drill bit, you can select the sizes you need. Shank size is 3/8" or less. Drilax tools will fit standard hand drills and press drills.

Pick any size 1", 1-3/16", 1-1/4", 1-3/8,", 1-1/2", 1-5/8", 1-3/4", 2", 2-3/8".

The diamond particule coating on DRILAX hole saws give superior performance and lifetime. Please note our tools do not need center pilot holes. Center pilot hole drills are mostly for wood, metal, etc.

Drilax tools can drill 1 " in depth.

Never let your drill bit run dry. Electroplated diamond coating will wear off if the tool gets too hot. Here is how you could use water to keep the tool cool:
a- You can build a mini water pool around the hole with plumbers putty.
b- You can choose to spray water on the drill bit.
c- Or you can use running water to cool the drill bit.

EASY TO USE

Center pilot drill bits are for wood, metal, etc.; Here is how you can keep the drill bit on target:
a- You can make your own guide out of plywood - plastic or even a card board. All you need is to keep the drill bit in place until it makes the initial marks.
b- You can start drilling at an angle, with the edge of the drill bit making a C slot and then getting the drill bit up to vertical.
c- You can manually guide the drill bit with wet sponge.

Please use protective gear.

Drilax has a drill bit guide available on Amazon. The guide has a suction base. Just search for "Drilax Drill Guide" on Amazon..
product_bullet_point:
HIGH QUALITY Diamond Coated Hole Saw Drill Bit Tool 1-1/4 inches Diameter
STANDARD 3/8 inch shank fits standard drill. DUSTLESS - FAST DRILLING Quartz, Granite, Ceramics, Porcelain, Tiles, Glass, Flower Pots, and More
SOLID STEEL BODY Spins True, Cools Down Easier, Holds Up Better

product_title: SoHoMiLL Electronic Door Knob with Backup Mechanical Key (Spring Latch Lock; Not Deadbolt; Not Phone Connected), Single Front keypad YL 99 B
product_description: WARNING!!! This is NOT a dead-bolt: when you press a valid code, you need to TURN the keypad knob to unlock within 3-sec while beeping! This is also a security feature "auto-lock" to prevent from "forgot-to-lock." This is a spring latch lock. The latch does NOT have motor and does NOT move itself. Therefore, it lasts longer than deadbolt. Again, You will need to TURN the keypad knob to unlock. Install this door knob yourself! Everything included: you just need a screwdriver, no professionals needed (saving on contractor costs)! Don't worry about losing, forgetting, or making extra keys time and time again. Fits in standard door knob installation hole. You're free to add, change, or delete user Codes. This lock works for exterior, interior, side, or garage entry doors. For family, each member can have their own user code to access. Coming home late at night? No problem. The keypad is lit up by LED when pressed, so you can see it in the dark. If relatives are visiting, set a temporary code for their stay. No spare keys needed. Going for a jog or a ride, no more carrying a bulky key chain or worrying about losing your keys along the way. Press your code and you are home. Pet lover: this lock will allow you to give your neighbor or pet sitter an User Code of their own while you are away. When you return, simply delete the code from the lock. For rental or vacation home owner, this will reduce your costs in replacing locks and making extra keys. Install this lock on your rental property and save yourself the hassle, too. When your renter moves out, simply delete or change the code.  Please note: While this door knob is designed for operational temperature from 6-degree F to 102-degree F in outdoor and indoor applications, it is recommended to be under a porch or some kind of overhead cover, and it should NOT DIRECTLY to be exposed to heavy rains or accumulated snow or melting ice. Please refer to photos in the listing and to our web site FAQs.

Quick release spring bars make it easy to swap straps in a matter of seconds without the need for tools. Swap regularly to compliment your wardrobe or mix and match with BARTON’s leather & silicone quick release bands to take your timepiece from the workplace to the gym.

Compatible with any watch (traditional or smart watch) that uses standard 18mm, 20mm or 22mm spring bars. To determine proper width, measure the width where current band attaches to the watch head.
Note that this band will fit hundreds of other traditional watches with standard 18mm, 19mm, 20mm, 21mm, 22mm, 23mm or 24mm lug widths.

SWAP IN SECONDS: Swap daily to compliment your wardrobe or mix and match with BARTON’s leather & silicone quick release bands to take your timepiece from the workplace to the gym. Simply slide quick release knob with finger as shown in diagram.

product_title: GoTags Personalized Dog Collar, Custom Embroidered with Pet Name and Phone Number in Blue, Black, Pink, Red and Orange, for Boy and Girl Dogs, 4 Adjustable Sizes, XSmall, Small, Medium, and Large
product_description:
Our personalized dog collars are made and shipped from the USA in 1-2 business days after an order is placed. Our shop is in Washington state. Don’t choose a collar from China that ships slowly overseas.

Durably made with comfort and function in mind, our long-lasting dog ID collar has:
smooth, tapered edges for a comfortable fit
strong, non-corrosive stainless steel D-ring for attaching tags and leash
high quality and secure side-release buckle for easy one handed release
5 collar colors to choose from: Blue, Black, Orange, Pink, and Red

Personalized Embroidery:
embroidery is permanently stitched through the collar for strength and long-lasting identification
15 embroidery thread color options to choose from for your personalized text
personalized text (e.g., dog name & phone number) limited to 25 characters maximum, including spaces
collars are personalized using all CAPITAL letters for legibility

Collar Sizing and Fit:
To determine the correct collar size for your dog, use a soft tape measure or piece of string and wrap it snugly around the base of your dog’s neck – snug enough so that you cannot fit any fingers under the measuring tape. Your pet’s measured neck size must fit within the collar’s adjustable length range. For instance, if your dog’s neck measures 13” inches order an 11”-16” inch adjustable collar.
4 adjustable collar sizes:
- XSmall (3/8” inch wide by 8”-12” inches in adjustable length)
- Small (5/8” inch wide by 11”-16” inches in adjustable length)
- Medium (3/4” inch wide by 14”-20” inches in adjustable length)
- Large (1” inch wide by 18”-26” inches in adjustable length)
please note: in some cases, when sizing the collar down there is a possibility that the adjustable slider could rest over some of the custom embroidery

English alphabet characters only.

product_title: Uttermara Sherpa Fleece Weighted Blanket 15lbs for Adults, Super Soft Cozy Fluffy Sherpa Flannel Sofa Bedding Throw Blanket, Twin Size Heavy Bed Blanket, 48 x 72 inches, Navy Blue
product_description:
Uttermara Sherpa Fleece Weighted Blanket features extra plush 220 GSM Sherpa and 220 GSM fleece that feels soft and smooth on the skin, keeping you warm over night.

Our Sherpa Sherpa Weighted Blanket is warm as wool and breathable as cotton, it makes the perfect bedding for excitable skins. This comfy and ultra-plush warm Sherpa blanket is with better fade & wrinkle resistance than cotton blankets, and won't bunch thanks to its microfiber texture. Just like you, your canine and feline friend will also find it irresistible.
product_bullet_point:
Unique Design Philosophy: The new Uttermara Sherpa weighted blanket doubles as a weighted blanket to support better / deeper sleep and a Sherpa fleece blanket featuring 220 GSM ultra-soft fleece top and 220 GSM plush Sherpa reverse to offer ultimate gentleness and warmth. Sewn together with decorative edging for a neat and complete look. This Sherpa blanket comes with better resistance to fade, stain, and wrinkles than cotton ones.
Sweetest Sleep Companion: Designed to offer natural deep and restful sleep for kids and adults with the feeling of being hugged, our weighted blanket is upgraded with Sherpa fleece material to add a luxurious fluffy touch to your sleep. Comfort & warmth maximized.
7 Layer Beads-Locking Design: Uttermara weighted blanket features a classic 7-layer design. The ceramic beads inside are as tiny as 1mm, and evenly distributed in small grids. 2 non-glue polyester and brushed fabric layers are used to secure the beads firmly, so the beads won't cluster or move around in the grids. No matter how much you toss and turn, the blanket hugs you all night long.
Select Your Blanket: Choose the weighted blanket weighs about 10-12% of your body weight plus 1 pound. This 15lbs weighted blanket is designed for adults weighing 140 - 190 lbs. Please keep in mind, it may take 7 - 14 days to get used to the blanket's weight. If you are not sure, start off with a lighter weight.
100% Satisfaction Guaranteed: We value our customers and take pride in providing the best shopping experience. You will enjoy our friendly customer service and a LIFETIME WARRANTY. If you are not happy with the purchase, please contact us, we will do our best to assist you.
